snippet: Cpl. Korey Nathan Pritchett was removed from embassy security detail after he consumed alcohol in the hours before reporting for duty in the Netherlands, where President Obama attended a summit meeting last month.
abstract: Marine Corps removes Cpl Korey Nathan Pritchett from embassy security detail after he broke a rule against consuming alcohol ahead of Pres Obama's arrival in the Netherlands.
